reviewText: Love the show and happy to get it. Great condition and got it on time.

I absolutely love this show! I am a bit late with the whole Mike&Molly viewing but I'm so glad that I caught on. I'm on to season 3 now. Great show and (to me) so very funny. And yes I love the Chicago accents!
This show is so much fun to watch. In my opinion the first two seasons were the best. These are difficult to find in stores too. I will watch these over and over.

Any fan of Mike and Molly will need to have all 5 seasons. The laughs never stop and the acting from all the cast is great. Everyone was perfectly cast and they never ran out of steam. When the show ended, I knew I would miss them. Owning all 5 seasons is one way to miss them a little less.
